@Comment:	Time is 0:06
@Comment:	MOT often reprimands Chi and Bro for misbehaving while the tape is running; another large chunk of the mealtime is Mot trying to get Chi to come back from tv room; Mot uses rather unusual logic sometimes , like telling Bro that if he doesn't sit right his food will go to one side of his body and he'll have trouble digesting it; Mot asks Chi if she's taking French at school; Chi says (perhaps falsely) no and Mot says she'll talk to the teacher and asks if Chi would prefer Spanish; but that's a very short exchange , so it's hard to tell what they were really talking about; children responsible for sweeping up crumbs under table
